              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">✔️</span>
                <span>详细的工具描述和使用场景说明</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">为您提供价值</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
